name: Remix Icon 2.5.0 component library (2200+ free icons)
description:
Last updated on May 24, 2022

------------------------------

Remix Icon is a set of open-source neutral-style system symbols elaborately crafted for designers and developers.

All 1200+ icons are free for both personal and commercial use.


All of the icons in this set are created and maintained by the Remix Design team at RemixIcon.


I converted these icons into components for my own use and thought that they might be useful to the community as well. All copyrights belong to RemixIcon.
